### Registering Lexical Nodes in Payload CMS Client Feature (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/rich-text/custom-features.mdx

This snippet demonstrates how to register custom Lexical nodes within a Payload CMS client-side feature. Nodes added here define how content is displayed and managed in the editor. The 'use client' directive is essential for client-side functionality.

```ts
'use client'\n\nimport { createClientFeature } from '@payloadcms/richtext-lexical/client'\nimport { MyNode } from './nodes/MyNode'\n\nexport const MyClientFeature = createClientFeature({\n  nodes: [MyNode],\n})
```

